The experiment is complete. All 7 tests for Conway's Game of Life are passing:

1. Empty grid returns empty array
2. Single live cell dies (underpopulation)
3. Two live cells die (underpopulation)
4. Block of four cells stays alive (still life)
5. Dead cell with 3 neighbors becomes alive (reproduction)
6. Live cell with >3 neighbors dies (overpopulation)
7. Blinker transforms to next generation (oscillator)
